n class=\"token keyword\">this<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.<\/span>books <span class=\"token operator\">=<\/span> <span class=\"token keyword\">await<\/span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.<\/span><span class=\"token function\">getBooks<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>page<span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export<\/span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default<\/span> Books<span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<p>Realizar atribui√ß√£o para uma chave de <code>params<\/code> causar√° um redirecionamento para a rota com os par√¢metros atualizados.<\/p>\n<p>Quando realizar atribui√ß√£o para um par√¢metro, o valor ser√° convertido para JSON antes de ser definido.<\/p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>üí° Redirecionamentos funcionam em lotes, ent√£o n√£o h√° perca de performance em multiplas atribui√ß√µes.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import<\/span> Nullstack <span class=\"token keyword\">from<\/span> <span class=\"token string\">'nullstack'<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class<\/span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Paginator<\/span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends<\/span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Nullstack<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">handleClick<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(<\/span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>params<span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span><\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>\n    params<span class=\"token punctuation\">.<\/span>filter <span class=\"token operator\">=<\/span> <span class=\"token string\">''<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n    params<span class=\"token punctuation\">.<\/span>page <span class=\"token operator\">=<\/span> <span class=\"token number\">1<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export<\/span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default<\/span> Paginator<span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<p>Atribuir uma string vazia a um par√¢metro ir√° remov√™-lo da url.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"segmentos-din-micos\"><a href=\"#segmentos-din-micos\">Segmentos Din√¢micos<\/a><\/h2><p>Parte da rota pode ser uma express√£o come√ßada com &quot;:&quot; segida por um nome de par√¢metro.<\/p>\n<p>Esse valor ser√° comparado com qualquer string na mesma posi√ß√£o de diret√≥rio.<\/p>\n<p>O valor da string na URL ser√° atribu√≠do para o <a href=\"/pt-br/contexto\">contexto<\/a>, par√¢metros e fun√ß√µes abaixo desse ponto na hierarquia ter√£o acesso a nova chave.<\/p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>üê±‚Äçüíª Abaixo um exemplo que visita &quot;/category/suspense?page=2&quot;:<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import<\/span> Nullstack <span class=\"token keyword\">from<\/span> <span class=\"token string\">'nullstack'<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class<\/span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Books<\/span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends<\/span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Nullstack<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">async<\/span> <span class=\"token function\">initiate<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(<\/span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>params<span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span><\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const<\/span> page <span class=\"token operator\">=<\/span> <span class=\"token function\">parseInt<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(<\/span>params<span class=\"token punctuation\">.<\/span>page<span class=\"token punctuation\">)<\/span> <span class=\"token operator\">||<\/span> <span class=\"token number\">1<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const<\/span> category <span class=\"token operator\">=<\/span> params<span class=\"token punctuation\">.<\/span>slug<span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">this<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.<\/span>books <span class=\"token operator\">=<\/span> <span class=\"token keyword\">await<\/span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.<\/span><span class=\"token function\">getBooks<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>category<span class=\"token punctuation\">,<\/span> page<span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export<\/span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default<\/span> Books<span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import<\/span> Nullstack <span class=\"token keyword\">from<\/span> <span class=\"token string\">'nullstack'<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import<\/span> Books <span class=\"token keyword\">from<\/span> <span class=\"token string\">'./Books'<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class<\/span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Application<\/span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends<\/span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Nullstack<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">render<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;<\/span>main<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">><\/span><\/span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;<\/span><span class=\"token class-name\">Books<\/span><\/span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">route<\/span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"<\/span>/category/:slug<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"<\/span><\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">><\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/<\/span>main<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">><\/span><\/span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export<\/span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default<\/span> Application<span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<p>Quando um segmento din√¢mico √© alterado, como por exemplo mover de &quot;/category/suspense&quot; para &quot;/category/comedy&quot;, o componente ser√° desfeito e uma nova inst√¢ncia ser√° criada.<\/p>\n<p>Mudar um par√¢metro de consulta n√£o re-instnaciar√° o componente.<\/p>\n<p>Os filhos do componente n√£o ser√£o re-instanciados automaticamente, voc√™ pode definir a mesma rota para os filhos ou fazer isso manualmente se desejar esse comportamento.<\/p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>üí° O comportamento mencionado acima resolve muitos dos problemas que voc√™ teria normalmente que lidar manualmente.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"curingas\"><a href=\"#curingas\">Curingas<\/a><\/h2><p>Curingas s√£o rotas declaradas com &quot;*&quot; como valor do atributo<\/p>\n<p>Essas rotas corresponder√£o a qualquer coisa se nada acima delas corresponder a URL requisitada.<\/p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import<\/span> Nullstack <span class=\"token keyword\">from<\/span> <span class=\"token string\">'nullstack'<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import<\/span> Home <span class=\"token keyword\">from<\/span> <span class=\"token string\">'./Home'<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class<\/span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Application<\/span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends<\/span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Nullstack<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">render<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(<\/span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>count<span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span><\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(<\/span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;<\/span>main<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">><\/span><\/span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;<\/span><span class=\"token class-name\">Home<\/span><\/span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">route<\/span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"<\/span>/<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"<\/span><\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/><\/span><\/span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;<\/span>div<\/span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">route<\/span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"<\/span>*<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"<\/span><\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">><\/span><\/span> Curinga <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/<\/span>div<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">><\/span><\/span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/<\/span>main<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">><\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)<\/span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span>\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<p>Curingas podem ser prefixados com um segmento.<\/p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>‚ú® Isso √© especialmente √∫til para engines que podem ser montadas em suas aplica√ß√µes.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import<\/span> Nullstack <span class=\"token keyword\">from<\/span> <span class=\"token string\">'nullstack'<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import<\/span> Home <span class=\"token keyword\">from<\/span> <span class=\"token string\">'./Home'<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import<\/span> BlogEngine <span class=\"token keyword\">from<\/span> <span class=\"token string\">'./BlogEngine'<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class<\/span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Application<\/span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends<\/span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Nullstack<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">render<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(<\/span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>count<span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span><\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(<\/span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;<\/span>main<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">><\/span><\/span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;<\/span><span class=\"token class-name\">Home<\/span><\/span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">route<\/span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"<\/span>/<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"<\/span><\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/><\/span><\/span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;<\/span><span class=\"token class-name\">BlogEngine<\/span><\/span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">route<\/span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"<\/span>/blog/*<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"<\/span><\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/><\/span><\/span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/<\/span>main<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">><\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)<\/span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span>\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<h2 id=\"roteador\"><a href=\"#roteador\">Roteador<\/a><\/h2><p>A chave <code>router<\/code> √© um proxy de objeto injetado em cada inst√¢ncia de cliente.<\/p>\n<p>O <code>router<\/code> tem tr√™s chaves:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code>url<\/code><\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong><code>path<\/code><\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong><code>base<\/code><\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>A chave <code>url<\/code> retorna tudo depois do dom√≠nio, incluindo o caminho e os par√¢metros de query como uma string.<\/p>\n<p>A chave <code>path<\/code> retorna apenas o caminho sem os par√¢metros de consulta.<\/p>\n<p>A chave <code>base<\/code> retorna apenas a url base (ex: <code>https://nullstack.app<\/code> ou <code>http://localhost:5000<\/code>).<\/p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>üí° As chaves acima automaticamente removem a barra final por conveni√™ncia.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p>Atribuir a <code>url<\/code> ou <code>path<\/code> causar√° redirecionamento.<\/p>\n<p>Atribuir uma url absoluta a <code>url<\/code> causar√° uma recarga completa.<\/p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import<\/span> Nullstack <span class=\"token keyword\">from<\/span> <span class=\"token string\">'nullstack'<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class<\/span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Application<\/span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends<\/span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Nullstack<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">prepare<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(<\/span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>router<span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span><\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(<\/span>router<span class=\"token punctuation\">.<\/span>path <span class=\"token operator\">==<\/span> <span class=\"token string\">'/'<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>\n      router<span class=\"token punctuation\">.<\/span>path <span class=\"token operator\">=<\/span> <span class=\"token string\">'/dashboard'<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span> <span class=\"token comment\">// simples mudan√ßa de rota<\/span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>\n      router<span class=\"token punctuation\">.<\/span>url <span class=\"token operator\">=<\/span> <span class=\"token string\">'https://my-domain.app'<\/span> <span class=\"token comment\">// recarga completa<\/span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span>\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<blockquote>\n<p>üí° Por baixo dos panos tags <code>a<\/code> e <code>params<\/code> usam o <code>router<\/code>.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"eventos-customizados\"><a href=\"#eventos-customizados\">Eventos customizados<\/a><\/h2><p>Atualizar <code>router.url<\/code> ou <code>router.path<\/code> ir√° gerar um evento personalizado.<\/p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import<\/span> Nullstack <span class=\"token keyword\">from<\/span> <span class=\"token string\">'nullstack'<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class<\/span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Analytics<\/span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends<\/span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Nullstack<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">hydrate<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(<\/span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>router<span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span><\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>\n    window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.<\/span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(<\/span>router<span class=\"token punctuation\">.<\/span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">,<\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)<\/span> <span class=\"token operator\">=><\/span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span>\n      console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.<\/span><span class=\"token function\">log<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(<\/span>router<span class=\"token punctuation\">.<\/span>url<span class=\"token punctuation\">)<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export<\/span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default<\/span> Analytics<span class=\"token punctuation\">;<\/span>\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<h2 id=\"-ncoras-especiais\"><a href=\"#-ncoras-especiais\">√Çncoras especiais<\/a><\/h2><p>Tags de √¢ncora aceitam somente alguns atributos especiais convenientes al√©m do <code>href<\/code> comum.<\/p>\n<p>Voc√™ pode atribuir o atributo <code>params<\/code> com um objeto como valor.<\/p>\n<p>O caminho permanecer√° o mesmo do caminho atual do roteador, mas os <code>params<\/code> ser√£o substitu√≠dos pelos novos par√¢metros que voc√™ especificar.<\/p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;<\/span>a<\/span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">params<\/span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span><span class=\"token literal-property property\">page<\/span><span class=\"token operator\">:<\/span> <span class=\"token number\">1<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span><\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">><\/span><\/span> Primeira <span class=\"token constant\">P<\/span>√°gina <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/<\/span>a<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">><\/span><\/span>\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<p>E voc√™ deseja apenas atualizar alguns par√¢metros e manter outros, voc√™ pode usar o operador JavaScript <em>spread<\/em> para isso.<\/p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;<\/span>a<\/span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">params<\/span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{<\/span><span class=\"token operator\">...<\/span>params<span class=\"token punctuation\">,<\/span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">page<\/span><span class=\"token operator\">:<\/span> <span class=\"token number\">1<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}<\/span><\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">><\/span><\/span> Primeira <span class=\"token constant\">P<\/span>√°gina <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/<\/span>a<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">><\/span><\/span>\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<p>Voc√™ pode definir o atributo <code>path<\/code> com uma string come√ßando com &quot;/&quot; e sem par√¢metros de query.<\/p>\n<p>Os par√¢metros permanecer√£o os mesmos, mas, o <code>path<\/code> ser√° atualizado.<\/p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;<\/span>a<\/span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">path<\/span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=<\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"<\/span>/category/suspense<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"<\/span><\/span><span class=\"token punctuation\">><\/spa